{"tid":1808384,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈 -> 黃色社區","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T14:25:33.000Z","uid":258118,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26bb92298f9c07df3226ba8fa8a97b619edf82d6","tid":1808384,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈咁有錢，但係而家好似特別係針對餐廳咁樣，我諗緊其實夠錢既話，最有本事個班黃色資本家可以係最黃既區分建立黃色社區，由住客，地主， 衣食住行，全部都係自己友，全部經濟收益都係幫緊自己人，又可以發展埋黃色旅遊業，向國際宣傳真正既香港。<br />\n<br />\n一開始可能一條街開始，之後慢慢發展開去。<br />\n<br />\n有d似&quot;海外小香港&quot; 既個concept, 係外國一條街攪條&quot;小香港&quot; 街咁樣。 <br />\n<br />\n咁樣好自然個區既區議員一定係黃，夠大既就自然連立法會都拎埋，慢慢做大佢應該幾正。<br />\n<br />\n當然有利有弊，歡迎討論。"},{"pid":"fafcf8fb1e246db505127726c86700f0f65d2554","tid":1808384,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:45:59.000Z","msg":"要呀<br />\n街，跟住小社區"},{"pid":"4bac28d3acc0796ce2f08590094d4b82907b296f","tid":1808384,"uid":78392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"黃色飲食圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e5755aa39435048c9a42489692772423696575","tid":1808384,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"我們都有一個夢想<br />\n<br />\n穩固黃色經濟圈成型 新系統迎接新模式<br />\n<br />\n抵制支付寶來襲，抗衡八達通賣港<br />\n<br />\n屬於我地新時代既支付系統。<br />\n[招兵買馬] <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1805119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1805119</a><br />\n[關注我們] <a href=\"https://t.me/TimesPayHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTimesPayHK&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=8ef327b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TimesPayHK</a>"},{"pid":"44d13ceb4a8f50f1f23c099c2442b506d19181b7","tid":1808384,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3726bee16ddc238fc2d6102325798fae298759","tid":1808384,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"良心生活圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E5%A4%9C-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E9%9B%A8%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E8%A6%81%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9C%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259B%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%259C%2588%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=3d376214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259B%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%259C%2588%2F&h=f82e7537\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E5%A4%9C-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E9%9B%A8%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E8%A6%81%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9C%88/</a><br />\n他又提到黃色經濟圈，但認為市民不應該只向錢看，未來要發展良心生活圈，「點解會被定黃藍，唔係播唔播《榮光》、派唔派水，其實係個心係咪支持呢班年青人、抗爭者。」<br />\n<br />\n張俊傑指，自己早前花了數十萬元成立「香港人嘅冰室資源分享中心」，起初只是希望作緊急援助，但後來發現，給予有需要人士工作機會更有意義，「我地需要俾佢哋係另一個角度，另一個香港，可以俾佢哋搵得到工作機會，搵得到一技之長。」<br />\n<br />\n他舉例，早前有20名髮型師教授了20名學徒，上五日課後聘請當中10位學徒在髮型屋工作；亦有Gel甲師開班教授學生，中心會免費提供場地及儀器，讓他們發揮所長，同時靠自己的勞力獲得收入。他認為，香港下一步要發展良心生活圈，透過不同行業的專才組成，讓青年人有一技之長，從而自給自足。"},{"pid":"3c40e7f76c41f8599725e833cce8d36484e42805","tid":1808384,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c3726bee16ddc238fc2d6102325798fae298759","tid":1808384,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"良心生活圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E5%A4%9C-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E9%9B%A8%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E8%A6%81%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9C%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259B%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%259C%2588%2F&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=3d376214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%259B%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%259C%2588%2F&h=f82e7537\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E5%A4%9C-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E9%9B%A8%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E9%BE%8D%E9%96%80%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E8%A6%81%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9C%88/</a><br />\n他又提到黃色經濟圈，但認為市民不應該只向錢看，未來要發展良心生活圈，「點解會被定黃藍，唔係播唔播《榮光》、派唔派水，其實係個心係咪支持呢班年青人、抗爭者。」<br />\n<br />\n張俊傑指，自己早前花了數十萬元成立「香港人嘅冰室資源分享中心」，起初只是希望作緊急援助，但後來發現，給予有需要人士工作機會更有意義，「我地需要俾佢哋係另一個角度，另一個香港，可以俾佢哋搵得到工作機會，搵得到一技之長。」<br />\n<br />\n他舉例，早前有20名髮型師教授了20名學徒，上五日課後聘請當中10位學徒在髮型屋工作；亦有Gel甲師開班教授學生，中心會免費提供場地及儀器，讓他們發揮所長，同時靠自己的勞力獲得收入。他認為，香港下一步要發展良心生活圈，透過不同行業的專才組成，讓青年人有一技之長，從而自給自足。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T14:25:33.000Z","msg":"好開始，但係社區既優勢係大家近大家，互相幫助，真係成個社區都係良心，當然，佢提出個種都可以做，但我覺得個impact無咁快同大"}]}